|| 📝 Word Counter ||

A simple tool that counts the number of words || characters || lines || in a given text.  
Perfect for beginners or anyone doing quick text analysis.

---

||  🚀 Features
- ✅ Count words
- ✅ Count characters (with or without spaces)
- ✅ Count lines
- ✅ Fast and easy to use

